      "span_text": "During our earlier experiments, we used an ad-hoc approach in setting the parameters of socio-cognitive populations: either by looking for an optimal configuration manually (e.g., checking the performances of different compositions by trial and error) or by basing it on the data from the human population [CITATION_1] ."
